WHY ADMIN / AI PRESSURE IS HIGH:
Children and family services span casework, safeguarding, referrals and programme reporting. Health and wellbeing delivery needs appointment coordination, clinical liaison and case records.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
