Care and supported living programmes require care plans, rotas, safeguarding and funder evidence. Advice services handle high-volume enquiries, case notes and referral tracking.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
Care charities face high data sensitivity. AI adoption is cautious; practical wins are usually in rota coordination, care note drafting support, and training rather than automated decision-making.

