WHAT THE ORGANISATION DOES:
A charity to provide children with the opportunity to have a full and rich childhood; through education and the acquiring of skills for life; through fun and creativity and through the love of God - we support local people making a difference in their locality - with a particular focus on the developing world.

ORGANISATION CONTEXT:
Ipswich, Suffolk, Suffolk. ~18 staff; income on record £560,000.

